headline: P&G to Webcast Discussion of First Quarter 25/26 Earnings Results on October 24
summary: CINCINNATI, September 26, 2025--The Procter & Gamble Company (NYSE:PG) will webcast a discussion of its first quarter earnings results on Friday, October 24, 2025, beginning at 8:30 a.m. ET.
